            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Petronia Erotis sibi et <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>T</abbr><ex>ito</ex></expan> Flavio Pharnaci kariss<supplied reason="lost">imo</supplied> <lb n="3"/>coniugi suo fecit et is quibus id ius pos<lb break="no" n="4"/>si dendi testamemto suo legavit <lb n="5"/>posterisque eorum <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibertis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>libertabus</abbr><ex>que</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/>in fronte <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>edes</ex></expan> <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> in agro <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>edes</ex></expan> XXV <lb n="7"/>et Zethi<supplied reason="lost">oni Artem</supplied>idori filio Rhodio itum ambi<lb break="no" n="8"/><expan><abbr>tu</abbr><ex>m</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>donav</abbr><ex>erunt</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>In sechs Fragmente gebrochen, von denen zwei verschollen sind. Z. 1 (Ende): möglicherweise noch ein Rest vom unteren Bogen des O erhalten.</p>
            </div>
